911
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:45,560
I ordered a few dishes

912
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:46,640
according to your preference.

913
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:48,880
Thank you for your thoughtfulness.

914
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:52,840
How has your mother been lately?

915
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:55,000
Is she feeling better?

916
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,040
Thank you for your concern.

917
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:58,880
Mother is very well.

918
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,840
Since you went home,

919
00:42:03,640 --> 00:42:04,840
