925
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:16,800
I do not have the confidence to return to the Yang residence yet.

926
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,520
Leave us.

927
00:42:24,680 --> 00:42:25,400
Yes.

928
00:42:32,240 --> 00:42:33,440
Is it because

929
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,680
